data.value: PremiumMed LLC is an exporter of world-famous brands to the Azerbaijani market of the largest manufacturers of medical laboratory equipment, reagents and consumables.

data.name: HeaderTitle
data.value: Thinking of you in quality and service!

data.name: MissionDesc
data.value: By analyzing the dynamics of the medical sector in the best possible way, to ensure long-term, unconditional customer satisfaction under the most favorable commercial conditions, to create loyal customers to our brands by equipping Azerbaijani laboratories with quality products that meet international standards in the world market. to provide our medical laboratories with the necessary equipment and products that will serve to improve the quality of life. To provide the best service to our valued customers, given that our past references are our commitment to our future work.

data.name: NotDifficult
data.value: It is not difficult to get our products!

data.name: QualityDesc
data.value: • Continuously improve the service in accordance with the requirements of our customers and the rules adopted by our health system in the sector in which we operate; To act in accordance with national and international laws, standards and regulatory requirements, • Ensuring sustainability and development, believing that quality can only be achieved through teamwork, working with partner clients in a team spirit and common sense approach, • To meet the current and future needs of our customers by investing in innovations in this area, to provide quality service with quality and safe products, to ensure unconditional customer satisfaction for the first time and every time, • Renew and develop itself to implement and improve the quality systems we have established, to ensure sustainability by investing in human resources. To ensure sustainable development of personnel in this field, to organize trainings, • Constantly monitor innovations in the health sector, increase market share and product range, ensure optimal efficiency and profitability, be among the sector leaders and be ahead of our competitors, • To provide a healthy and safe work environment for the company's employees, to strengthen the sense of corporate belonging by increasing training, communication and motivation opportunities, • Assess the factors and conditions that affect the health and safety of all people affected by the activities of our company (employees, temporary workers, subcontractors, visitors, customers and anyone in the workplace) and take the necessary measures, • To raise awareness about the environment, to contribute to its protection and development.

data.name: VisionDesc
data.value: Adhering to the principles of quality, reliability, human health, prestige, customer satisfaction, to serve customers in accordance with world standards, diversifying and improving service. Become a consumer of medical laboratory products that offer the widest range of products in their field, with the highest market share with professional investments and a professional, dynamic team.

data.name: we who?
data.value: PremiumMed LLC, a medical laboratory established in Baku in March 2016 the largest manufacturers of equipment, reagents and consumables, is an exporter of world-famous brands to the Azerbaijani market. Proven in this area using technology and innovation, dynamic and, despite its young age is a young and independent company full of wonderful ideas. The most important and significant of the company - the key activities, sales of laboratory products and services, project activities, Perfect implementation of methodological and service support of clinics.
